---
layout: layouts/component-demo.njk
title: Watermark
description: a decorative repeating overlay text or image marking a page
---

{% from "components/watermark/macro.njk" import watermark %}

<h2>Text watermark</h2>
{% call watermark({ text: "CONFIDENTIAL", gap: "120px", rotate: -22 }) %}
  <div style="background: var(--nhsuk-white); padding: 2rem; min-height: 12rem;">
    <p>Underlying content. The watermark layer sits beneath this content visually
    (consumer applies the repeating-pattern CSS via the `data-text` attribute).</p>
  </div>
{% endcall %}

<h2>Default rotation and gap</h2>
{% call watermark({ text: "DRAFT" }) %}
  <div style="background: var(--nhsuk-white); padding: 2rem;">
    <p>Default values: gap 100px, rotate -22 degrees.</p>
  </div>
{% endcall %}
